{"name":"A Book of Boiling Blood","permission":{"default":0,"xVCY8TaEyq1Er5RJ":3},"type":"misc","data":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p>You may open and read from this book once a day. Your enemy must make a DR12 test to prevent this. If they fail D2 Berserker-slayers (see page 60) appear from the depths of a forgotten dimension of blood. Roll a D6.</p>\n<p>On a 1&ndash;4 these creatures fight alongside you. On a 5&ndash;6 they turn on you, attempting to kill you and destroy the book. After the battle they return to their imprisonment.</p>","carryWeight":1,"equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/icons/classitems/bookofboilingblood.png","effects":[],"_id":"28N6nQMghCF6nG4e"}
{"name":"Speaker of Truths","permission":{"default":0,"xVCY8TaEyq1Er5RJ":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":"<p>Twice per day use your wisdom, knowledge, advice and inner calm to bring clarity to a creature of your choice. The DR of the next test they undertake is lowered by 4.</p>","rollFormula":"","rollLabel":""},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/esoteric_hermit.png","effects":[],"_id":"Frumgt22ogs8W7Bk"}
{"name":"Master of Fate","permission":{"default":0,"xVCY8TaEyq1Er5RJ":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":"<p>What use are maps when the substance of causality itself is open to you? You know the right way with a DR8 Presence test.</p>","rollFormula":"1d20+@abilities.presence.value","rollLabel":"Know"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/esoteric_hermit.png","effects":[],"_id":"HVtEy2VmsOh5aBOE"}
{"name":"Initiate of the Invisible College","permission":{"default":0,"xVCY8TaEyq1Er5RJ":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":"<p>Once per day you may summon D2 scrolls, whose power can be used only once. Roll a d4, on a 1&ndash;2 the scrolls are sacred, on a 3&ndash;4, unclean. If the scrolls are not used before sunrise they turn to ash.</p>","rollFormula":"","rollLabel":""},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/esoteric_hermit.png","effects":[],"_id":"YZMYPQQaZk4p3Neu"}
