{"name":"Esoteric Hermit","permission":{"default":0,"xVCY8TaEyq1Er5RJ":3},"type":"class","data":{"abilities":"<p>Wise, roll 3D6+2 for Presence. Weak, roll 3D6&minus;2 for Strength. Ordinary starting equipment plus one random scroll (sacred or unclean). Roll a D4 on the weapons table and D2 on the armor table. You also begin with one of the following:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Master of Fate</li>\n<li>Book of Boiling Blood</li>\n<li>Speaker of Truths</li>\n<li>Initiate of the Invisible College</li>\n<li>Bard of the Undying</li>\n<li>Hawk as Weapon</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Eldritch Origins, d6</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Awakening, adult, in a ritual circle underneath the northern bridge to Grift.</li>\n<li>Wandered, memoryless, from the mouth of a cavern at the cliffs of Terion.</li>\n<li>Single child survivor of an incident in the Valley of the Unfortunate Undead.</li>\n<li>Dying of plague in a Bergen Chrypt hovel, you touched something from outside.</li>\n<li>An average individual until you encountered something in a dim glade in Sarkash.</li>\n<li>Raised on a lonely island in Lake Onda. No one else has ever heard of this island and you can&rsquo;t return.</li>\n</ol>","armorTableDie":"1d2","description":"The stone of your cave is one with the stars. Silence and perfection. Now the chaos of a fallen world disturbs your rituals and the caul of night grows blacker than your cavernâ€™s gloom. Irritating!","omenDie":"1d4","startingAgility":"3d6","startingHitPoints":"1d4","startingItems":"","startingPresence":"3d6+2","startingRolls":"morkborg.random-scrolls,All Scrolls,1\nmorkborg.rolls-esoteric-hermit,Esoteric Hermit Items,1\nmorkborg.rolls-esoteric-hermit,Eldritch Origins,1","startingSilver":"1d6*10","startingStrength":"3d6-2","startingToughness":"3d6","weaponTableDie":"1d4"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/esoteric_hermit.png","effects":[],"_id":"ifSBk6ORiHgq3Xhr"}
